{"content":"<div id=\"Ps.120\" class=\"chapter\">\n<h3 class=\"d\">上行（或譯登階，下同）之詩。</h3>\n<h3 class=\"s\">求主恩助</h3>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v1\"><sup id=\"Ps.120.1\" class=\"v1\">1</sup>我在急難中求告耶和華，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v1\">他就應允我。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v2\"><sup id=\"Ps.120.2\" class=\"v2\">2</sup>耶和華啊，求你救我脫離</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v2\">說謊的嘴唇和詭詐的舌頭！</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v3\"><sup id=\"Ps.120.3\" class=\"v3\">3</sup>詭詐的舌頭啊，他會給你甚麼呢？</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v3\">會加給你甚麼呢？</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v4\"><sup id=\"Ps.120.4\" class=\"v4\">4</sup>就是勇士的利箭、</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v4\">羅騰木的炭火。</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v5\"><sup id=\"Ps.120.5\" class=\"v5\">5</sup>禍哉！我寄居在<span class=\"pn\">米設</span>，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v5\">住在<span class=\"pn\">基達</span>帳棚之中。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v6\"><sup id=\"Ps.120.6\" class=\"v6\">6</sup>我與那恨惡和平的人</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v6\">許久同住。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v7\"><sup id=\"Ps.120.7\" class=\"v7\">7</sup>我願和平，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v7\">當我發言，他們卻要戰爭。</span></p>\n</div>\n"}